00614 static inline int_fast8_t ilog2(uint32_t x)
00615 {
00616     if (is_constant(x))
00617         return ((x) & (1ULL << 31) ? 31 :
00618             (x) & (1ULL << 30) ? 30 :
00619             (x) & (1ULL << 29) ? 29 :
00620             (x) & (1ULL << 28) ? 28 :
00621             (x) & (1ULL << 27) ? 27 :
00622             (x) & (1ULL << 26) ? 26 :
00623             (x) & (1ULL << 25) ? 25 :
00624             (x) & (1ULL << 24) ? 24 :
00625             (x) & (1ULL << 23) ? 23 :
00626             (x) & (1ULL << 22) ? 22 :
00627             (x) & (1ULL << 21) ? 21 :
00628             (x) & (1ULL << 20) ? 20 :
00629             (x) & (1ULL << 19) ? 19 :
00630             (x) & (1ULL << 18) ? 18 :
00631             (x) & (1ULL << 17) ? 17 :
00632             (x) & (1ULL << 16) ? 16 :
00633             (x) & (1ULL << 15) ? 15 :
00634             (x) & (1ULL << 14) ? 14 :
00635             (x) & (1ULL << 13) ? 13 :
00636             (x) & (1ULL << 12) ? 12 :
00637             (x) & (1ULL << 11) ? 11 :
00638             (x) & (1ULL << 10) ? 10 :
00639             (x) & (1ULL <<  9) ?  9 :
00640             (x) & (1ULL <<  8) ?  8 :
00641             (x) & (1ULL <<  7) ?  7 :
00642             (x) & (1ULL <<  6) ?  6 :
00643             (x) & (1ULL <<  5) ?  5 :
00644             (x) & (1ULL <<  4) ?  4 :
00645             (x) & (1ULL <<  3) ?  3 :
00646             (x) & (1ULL <<  2) ?  2 :
00647             (x) & (1ULL <<  1) ?  1 :
00648             (x) & (1ULL <<  0) ?  0 :
00649             ilog2_undefined());
00650 
00651     return 31 - clz(x);
00652 }
